textBeforeTable: Find Detroit Tigers Tickets Their loyal fans have continued to support them and purchase Detroit Tigers tickets to see them play in person. They have always had faith in their team and are now seeing the positive results. The Tigers are on their way to what could be their best season since the first half of the 20th century. There are many new rising stars on the team that are helping bring the team to a post-season. With the help of the veteran players, they are surprising the baseball community with the teams' ability to win games. They have been hitting home runs, pitching strike outs and making amazing defensive plays. With a difficult couple of series coming up the Detroit Tigers will continue their rising success to make sure that they can take it all the way to the World Series. Detroit Tiger fans have stuck with them through thick and thin and are now being rewarded. The team has also adopted a new following of fans that are extremely pleased with their choice of team. Comerica Park may be one of the older baseball stadiums, but it is one that you want to see. It has old school charm and reminds you of what baseball really is.
